cule chemistry. Further quantification\nof these pathways will help astrochemical models to constrain their relative\ncontribution to the interstellar budget of, especially, the organic species\nH2CO and HNCO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2020 20:45:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
