 one waveguide to numerous optical ring resonators as\npassive nanophotonic switches. With our strategy, we achieve accurate on-demand\nlight localization while avoiding spatial demanding bundles of waveguides and\ndemonstrate the feasibility of a proof of concept device and its additional\nscalability, towards high resolution and low damaging neural optoelectrodes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2020 23:36:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-04"}
