 dependence of the ratio ${\\cal M}_D/T$\nshows a very similar behavior as that found in lattice simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2020 08:36:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 08:43:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 25 Apr 2021 11:59:47 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 21 Sep 2021 02:31:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
