$, we provide,\nin an optimal way, a higher-order approximation of global mild solutions to PKS\nequation if the initial density has a finite second moment. All convergence\nrates studied in this article are under the $L^p$-norm with $p \\in [1,\\infty]$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2020 09:47:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-04"}
