cts are priced lower than the lower-value\nproducts when the private valuations are exponentially distributed. Finally,\nthe web-based interface generally achieves higher profits for the seller than a\nVA due to the greater commitment power inherent in its presentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2020 22:05:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-09"}
